<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Accès refusé — Docly</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/build/app.css">
    <style>
        @keyframes fadeUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
            to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: #FF701F;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
            max-width: 480px;
            width: 100%;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
            animation: fadeUp 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) both;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .icon-wrap {
            width: 5rem;
            height: 5rem;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #fff7ed;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
        }
        .icon-wrap i {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #FF701F;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #111827;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .plan-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            background: #fff7ed;
            border: 1.5px solid #fed7aa;
            color: #ea580c;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.9rem;
            background: #FF701F;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background 0.2s;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover { background: #e05e10; }
        .btn-secondary {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.9rem;
            background: #f3f4f6;
            color: #374151;
            border-radius: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-secondary:hover { background: #e5e7eb; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="icon-wrap">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-lock"></i>
        </div>

        <h1>403</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
            Vous n'avez pas accès à cette fonctionnalité.<br>
            Passez à un plan supérieur pour en profiter.
        </p>

        {% if app.user %}
            <div class="plan-badge">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-tag"></i>
                Plan actuel&nbsp;: {{ app.user.plan ? app.user.plan.name : 'FREE' }}
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        <a href="/pricing" class="btn-primary">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up" style="margin-right:0.4rem;"></i>
            Voir les offres
        </a>
        <a href="/convert" class="btn-secondary">
            Retour aux outils
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
